short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: LyricTuneYT is a browser extension that enhances your YouTube experience by displaying lyrics for the current videos you're watching

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: LyricTuneYT is your dedicated lyrics companion for YouTube, designed with a single purpose in mind: to effortlessly provide accurate lyrics for the music you love. With a seamless integration into YouTube videos, this Chrome extension offers real-time lyric search, ensuring you never miss a word of your favorite songs.
